title: #92Noon! Gorg&Arrigoni/Games/Gleeman
description: Kevin Gorg and Brian Arrigoni are in studio during the first hour to tackle hardcore Wild & high school hockey, Nordo workshops a new game called "Stump the Snob" with Ron Johnson & Pat Micheletti competing against PA(the sports Snob), then Gleeman is in studio the final hour on hoops and Twins.
